: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"#plugin-categories\">↑ Back to Plugin Categories</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"best-site-migration-plugin\">Best Site Migration Plugins</h2>\n<p>Ever wanted to build your WordPress site in your local development environment or on a staging server then migrate it to a live WordPress site. Then you need a site migration plugin and the best one without a doubt is <a href=\"https://deliciousbrains.com/wp-migrate-db-pro/\">WP DB Migrate</a> by Brad Tournard and the <a href=\"https://deliciousbrains.com/\">Delicious Brains</a> team.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://deliciousbrains.com/wp-migrate-db-pro/\">WP DB Migrate</a></strong> <span class=\"label label-success\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-migrate-db/\">Free Version</a></span> <span class=\"label label-primary\"><a href=\"https://deliciousbrains.com/wp-migrate-db-pro/\">Pro Version</a></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://deliciousbrains.com/wp-migrate-db-pro/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3763 size-full\" src=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250.jpg\" alt=\"Best Site Migration Plugin\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250.jpg 772w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-400x130.jpg 400w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-768x249.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"#plugin-categories\">↑ Back to Plugin Categories</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"security-plugins\">Best Security Plugins</h2>\n<p>Security is a very important aspect to any WordPress site. Since WordPress is so popular it&#8217;s a very big target. So with that said you&#8217;d better have some way to protect your WordPress website. While some host have some sort of security layer you&#8217;ll probably want to take some extra steps to harden your website.</p>\n<p>I personally use <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/\"